{"title":"日本人民反美大示威赞——调寄“大拍遍”","authors":["赵朴初"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":1,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本人民反美大示威赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——调寄“大拍遍”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵朴初"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刮地风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲天炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈山雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破城潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多摩川①，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗飞焰火云烧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横须贺②，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼声卷海浪花摇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍山遥水遥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽贤豪俊豪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展龙韬虎韬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗狂涛恶涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜心招手招，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共吾曹汝曹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑狐妖鬼妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看头焦尾焦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边厢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碰上了年头不妙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边厢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同样糟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十指头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按跳蚤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问几天安稳坐皇朝？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慢逍遥；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不听："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“滚出亚洲！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“滚出非洲！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更高呼“滚出冲绳岛！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不见："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近从后院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远到重洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正四方八面来风暴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"①多摩川——本月二十六日日本东京十二万五千人群众大会在横田美空军基地附近多摩川河滩上举行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"②横须贺——日本港口，是美国在日本的最大海军基地。（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬滚回去！（木刻）            吴祖望"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}